              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  By definition, <fr:link href="/schm-2LXR/" title="Closed and universally closed maps of schemes" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-2LXR/" display-uri="schm-2LXR" type="local">universally closed</fr:link> maps are closed under pullbacks of schemes.
